name: CozyCat Bed
description: The CozyCat Bed from FelineComfort offers your cat a plush, comfortable place to rest. Made from soft, durable materials, this bed is perfect for cats of all sizes. Easy to clean and machine washable.

description: Keep your cat entertained with the WhiskerToys Play Set. Includes a variety of toys such as balls, mice, and feathers to stimulate your cat's natural hunting instincts. Safe and non-toxic materials.

name: Purrfect Grooming Kit

name: KittySafe Litter Box
